Even if you're kinda hesitant to get on them, so long as you commit even the smallest amount of bravery to riding it, you pretty much conquer the entire thing by default. You get pushed through the line. They lock you into the seat. The ride literally forces you to move forward through the actual ups and downs of the experience. Screaming is encouraged!
